<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Santa_Clara_Systems&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Santa Clara Systems (page does not exist)">Santa Clara Systems, Inc.</a> (1986)</li>
